data.title: Marijan Davor - Storm - Oluja Engleski
data.meta_description: Marijan Davor - Storm - Oluja Engleski  - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is the table of contents for a book titled "Storm" by Davor Marijan. It provides an overview of the liberation military-police operation Storm conducted by Croatian armed forces in August 1995 that brought an end to the occupation of Croatian territory by Serbian forces. The book presents the preparation and course of the operation chronologically based on available historical sources from each corps district of the Croatian armed forces. It aims to provide the first historical analysis of Operation Storm while acknowledging limitations from the availability of sources.
